    "In Sect. 3, the methodology, based on the PRISMA (Preferred Reporting Items for Systematic Reviews and Meta-Analyses) guidelines, is described.",
    "In Sect. 4, the taxonomy used in this review, related to CH and its characteristics, the experience, the iVR design, and the evaluation are all detailed.",
